in Easy Login &#38; Register, the new [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4320:\"<p>In the last years, due to the addition of more plugins to our catalog and the improvement of many of those already available, the economic value of our CLUB has increased a lot and, as a consequence, the number of people using it.</p>\n<p>The release of the new plugin <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/a-new-login-register-plugin-to-reduce-the-cart-abandonment-rate/\"><em>Easy Login &amp; Register</em></a>, the new design of <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/not-just-an-update-a-brand-new-redesign-for-yith-gift-cards-plugin/\"><em>Gift Card</em></a> and <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wishlist-3-0-is-now-available/\"><em>Wishlist</em></a> and the upcoming addition of the <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-point-of-sale-for-woocommerce/\"><em>Point of Sale (POS)</em></a> plugin to our catalog are only the starting points of what will let us step-up the quality of all our products throughout next year.</p>\n<h2>Offer our customers the best plugins for WooCommerce on the market</h2>\n<p>On one hand, our long-term plan is to provide a high-quality support service and, on the other hand, to offer our customers the best plugins for WooCommerce on the market. Not only in terms of features, usability, and design but also on performance, an essential aspect for those people managing e-commerce sites. For this reason, we have hired <strong>a team of experts</strong> that will guide us through the <strong>optimization of our framework</strong> to improve the performance of some of our plugins (loading time, reduction of both the number of calls to DB and number of queries).</p>\n<p>To grant all of this to the many loyal customers we gained over the years and those that will join the YITH family in the future, it is important for us to find a new organizational set-up to employ our workforce and our energy in the best possible way.</p>\n<p>A few days ago, we had a round-table meeting and carefully analyzed our valued users. 90% of our customers joining the Club are developers, mainly freelancers, and e-commerce owners that use 2-3 licenses per plugin at the most. 10% is related to medium/big web agencies that use all 30 licenses available per plugin.</p>\n<p>So far, both customer types have paid the same amount to join the CLUB.<br />\nAt first, we thought about just increasing the CLUB price for all new subscribers, without differences of any sort. Yet, we didn&#8217;t want this change to be seen as discriminating against the 90% of members who use only a few licenses of our plugins and have a more limited budget.</p>\n<p>We have, therefore, decided to safeguard these customers by offering them a plan (that we will call &#8220;Business&#8221;) at the same price as the current one, reducing only the number of licenses available, giving that many were left unused anyway.</p>\n<p>So, we will create another plan (“Agency”) to grant a fair value of the Club for our niche of customers, that is the 10% that usually uses most of the 30 licenses available. As a consequence, this takes a heavier workload at our support desk, conversely to members using only a few licenses.</p>\n<h2>January 20, 2020, our YITH CLUB will be available in two different plans</h2>\n<p>So, to recap: from <strong>January 20, 2020</strong>, our <strong>YITH CLUB</strong> will be available in two different plans:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>the “Business” plan with <strong>6 licenses available per each plugin</strong> for the yearly price of <strong><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\"><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\"><span class=\'currency-symbol\'>&euro;</span><span></span>&nbsp;499</span><span class=\'decimals\'>,99</span></span></strong>;</li>\n<li>the “Agency” plan with <strong>30 licenses available per each plugin</strong> for the yearly price of <strong><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\"><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\"><span class=\'currency-symbol\'>&euro;</span><span></span>&nbsp;999</span><span class=\'decimals\'>,99</span></span></strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We would like to specify that <strong>this change will affect new members only</strong>. Customers who have already subscribed to our Club will remain on the same plan until the moment they decide to cancel the current one and start a new subscription.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/new-club-membership-plans-from-2020/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"Wishlist 3.0 is now available: discover the new design and the powerful features\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wishlist-3-0-is-now-available/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wishlist-3-0-is-now-available/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 10 Dec 2019 10:45:35 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"YITH News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1102127\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:340:\"We know that many of YITH customers wished for a new style of our plugins for a while so as to benefit from more beautiful, usable and functioning interfaces. And since ever, our customers&#8217; wishes are our priority. The same goes for any e-commerce that wants to loyalize customers and increase conversions: for those selling [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Alessio\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12946:\"<p>We know that many of YITH customers wished for a new style of our plugins for a while so as to benefit from more beautiful, usable and functioning interfaces.</p>\n<p>And <b>since ever, our customers&#8217; wishes are our priority</b>.</p>\n<p>The same goes for any e-commerce that wants to loyalize customers and increase conversions: for those selling online, it is essential to know what purchasers expect to be able to create focused offers and encourage users to buy.</p>\n<p>This is why you can&#8217;t do without our plugin YITH WooCommerce Wishlist, which is available in the brand new version 3.0, especially now that Christmas is just around the corner.</p>\n<p>Every e-commerce offers customers the possibility to create wishlists with the products they want. The wishlist in e-commerce has become a basic functionality, a must-have for users who want to &#8220;save&#8221; their favorite products and find them quickly and easily to purchase them at a later time.</p>\n<p>Or to share them with relatives and friends when a birthday, Christmas and other events approach. According to statistics, 37% of users who usually purchase online, share their wishlist on social media and/or with their loved ones, with the hope to receive one of the products available on the list as a gift.</p>\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t implemented a wishlist in your e-commerce yet, take a look at the features of our Wishlist 3.0 and install it on your store right now!</p>\n<p><b>What options have we added and improved in Wishlist 3.0?</b></p>\n<h3>1- We have made the administration panel more usable</h3>\n<p>Now it&#8217;s easier to spot the options and configure the plugin even for those who still don&#8217;t know our framework or don&#8217;t have specific technical skills.</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-1102130 size-large aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-1024x726.jpg\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist new panel\" width=\"1024\" height=\"726\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-1024x726.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-300x213.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-768x545.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-1536x1089.jpg 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-261x185.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-311x221.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-363x257.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello-270x191.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/pannello.jpg 1660w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h2>2- We have made the interface more innovative</h2>\n<p>Just like <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/not-just-an-update-a-brand-new-redesign-for-yith-gift-cards-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YITH Gift Cards</a>, YITH Wishlist needed renewal too. We have, therefore, designed a new interface that your customers will find appealing and intuitive.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1102132 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-1024x582.jpg\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist - New layout\" width=\"1024\" height=\"582\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-1024x582.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-300x171.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-768x437.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-1536x873.jpg 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-261x148.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-311x177.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-363x206.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout-270x153.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/layout.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h2>3- Different layouts to choose from</h2>\n<p>We have added different layouts, both for the wishlist page and the content shown in the single wishlist, to make the creation and consultation more interesting.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1102133 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-1024x534.png\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist - Different layouts\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-1024x534.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-300x156.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-768x401.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-261x136.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-311x162.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-363x189.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009-270x141.png 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/009.png 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h2>4- Advanced management of the wishlist from the user side</h2>\n<p>Your customers can benefit from the complete management of their wishlists. We have enhanced some features already available in the plugin (such as the possibility to create unlimited wishlists or share them on social media) and added the possibility to download wishlists as a PDF, track product prices, configure their quantity, sort the products in the list by drag and drop.</p>\n<p>Everything that makes the consultation and use of the wishlist easier for the customer is now available in this new update.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1102134 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-1024x480.jpg\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist Management\" width=\"1024\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-1024x480.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-300x141.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-768x360.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-1536x720.jpg 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-2048x960.jpg 2048w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-261x122.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-311x146.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-363x170.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-270x127.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h2>5- A “wishlist” widget to use in the header or the sidebar</h2>\n<p>Through the widget, users can benefit from an overview of the products they have in the wishlist and access it easily and directly with a single click.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1102135\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010.png\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist widget\" width=\"851\" height=\"676\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010.png 851w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010-300x238.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010-768x610.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010-261x207.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010-311x247.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010-363x288.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/010-270x214.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" /></p>\n<h2>6- Possibility to send automatic emails to customers when a product is back in stock or on sale.</h2>\n<p>We have added an option to catch your customers&#8217; attention and encourage them to come back to your e-commerce.</p>\n<p>From version 3.0, you can enable the automatic sending of emails to inform users when a product in their wishlist that was out-of-stock is available again and when a product of their wishlist has a discounted price.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1102136 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-1024x425.jpg\" alt=\"YITH Wihslist page\" width=\"1024\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-1024x425.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-300x124.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-768x318.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-1536x637.jpg 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-2048x849.jpg 2048w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-261x108.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-311x129.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-363x150.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/email-270x112.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h2>7-  A better procedure to send promotional emails</h2>\n<p>Before sending promotional emails to users who have added specific products to their wishlist, you will be able to open a modal window to customize the email through the editor and see a preview.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1102137 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007.png\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist Email\" width=\"936\" height=\"676\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007.png 936w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007-300x217.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007-768x555.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007-261x189.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007-311x225.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007-363x262.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/007-270x195.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px\" /></p>\n<h2>8- Possibility to customize the Ask for an estimate form</h2>\n<p>With this update, we have added the possibility to customize the Ask for an estimate form to choose what and how many required fields users must complete.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1102138 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-1024x1010.jpg\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist estimate\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1010\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-1024x1010.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-65x65.jpg 65w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-300x296.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-768x757.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-1536x1515.jpg 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-261x257.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-311x307.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-363x358.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-270x266.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-100x100.jpg 100w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate-80x80.jpg 80w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/estimate.jpg 1582w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h2>9- A better performance on mobile devices</h2>\n<p>We have also improved wishlists&#8217; appearance and functionality for users who browse and purchase through mobile devices (essential aspect as most of the users purchase from a smartphone or tablet).</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1102139 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-1024x890.jpg\" alt=\"YITH Wishlist Mobile\" width=\"1024\" height=\"890\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-1024x890.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-300x261.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-768x668.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-261x227.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-311x270.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-363x316.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile-270x235.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/mobile.jpg 1277w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>Have a look at the complete <a href=\"https://docs.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/changelog/changelog-premium-version/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">changelog</a> and try out our <a href=\"https://plugins.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">new demo</a> to find out all the features available in the new plugin version. To learn more about it, you can also refer to the<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> landing page</a>.</p>\n<p>What do you think about this update? We&#8217;ll be waiting for your precious feedback! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wishlist-3-0-is-now-available/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:26:\"https://yithemes.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\"